      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate the BGE M3 inference API, start by configuring the endpoint with appropriate authentication and network settings. Use containerization tools like Docker for consistent deployment across environments. Ensure your API gateway handles rate limiting and request validation to prevent overload. For example, set up health checks to monitor API availability and implement retry logic for transient failures."
          }
